[B]Command roots[/B]
[LIST]
[*]Player: [ICODE]/f[/ICODE] (aliases: [ICODE]/faction[/ICODE], [ICODE]/factions[/ICODE])
[*]Admin: [ICODE]/fa[/ICODE] (alias: [ICODE]/factionadmin[/ICODE])
[/LIST]

[B]Configuration and operations[/B]
[LIST]
[*]Generated files: [ICODE]config.yml[/ICODE], [ICODE]database.yml[/ICODE], [ICODE]messages.yml[/ICODE], [ICODE]gui.yml[/ICODE]
[*]Storage support: embedded H2 or MySQL/MariaDB
[*]Operations docs available for rollout, troubleshooting, and scaling
[/LIST]

[B]Migration-oriented for existing communities[/B]
If your network comes from legacy Factions servers, PvPIndex Factions is built to keep the familiar gameplay loop while giving you a cleaner and more future-proof backend.

